}}[[Classes]]: <u>InterpolationSpecial</u>

An '''interpolation special''' triggers its special whenever an [[Classes:InterpolationPoint|interpolation point]] with the same TID is used by any of the moving objects ([[Classes:ActorMover|ActorMover]], [[Classes:MovingCamera|MovingCamera]] or [[Classes:PathFollower|PathFollower]]).
==== [[DECORATE]] definition ====
 ACTOR <u>InterpolationSpecial</u> native
 {
   +{{Flag|NOBLOCKMAP}}
   +{{Flag|NOSECTOR}}
   +{{Flag|NOGRAVITY}}
   +{{Flag|DONTSPLASH}}
 }
